---
import BaseLayout from "../layouts/BaseLayout.astro";
import { withBase } from "../lib/paths";

const homeUrl = new URL(withBase("/"), Astro.site ?? Astro.url.origin).toString();
const profileStructuredData = {
    "@context": "https://schema.org",
    "@type": "ProfilePage",
    name: "祝庆 Zhu Qing | 影视后期与 Unreal Engine 开发",
    url: homeUrl,
    description: "祝庆的个人作品集首页，聚焦影视后期、UE5、虚拟制片、MetaHuman 与视觉设计。",
    mainEntity: {
        "@type": "Person",
        name: "祝庆",
        alternateName: "Zhu Qing",
        email: "mailto:zq_eugene@qq.com",
        jobTitle: "Film and Television Technology Student",
        knowsAbout: ["Unreal Engine", "MetaHuman", "Post-Production", "Virtual Production", "Color Grading"],
    },
};
---

<BaseLayout
    title="祝庆 Zhu Qing | 影视后期与 Unreal Engine 开发"
    description="祝庆的个人作品集首页，聚焦影视后期、UE5、虚拟制片、MetaHuman 与视觉设计。"
    activePath="/"
    preloadImage="/images/home/zq.webp"
    structuredData={profileStructuredData}
>
    <main class="home-hero">
        <div class="home-grid">
            <section class="profile-col" data-reveal>
                <div class="cinematic-frame">
                    <img src={withBase("/images/home/zq.webp")} alt="祝庆 Zhu Qing cinematic portfolio still" loading="eager" fetchpriority="high" />
                </div>

                <p class="eyebrow" data-i18n-cn="影视技术 / UE Development" data-i18n-en="Film Technology / UE Development">影视技术 / UE Development</p>
                <h1>
                    <span data-i18n-cn="祝庆" data-i18n-en="Zhu Qing">祝庆</span>
                    <small data-i18n-cn="Zhu Qing" data-i18n-en="Film Tech / UE Developer">Zhu Qing</small>
                </h1>
                <div class="hero-actions" aria-label="快速入口" data-aria-cn="快速入口" data-aria-en="Quick links">
                    <a class="hero-action" href={withBase("/portfolio")} data-i18n-cn="查看作品" data-i18n-en="View Works">查看作品</a>
                    <a class="hero-action" href={withBase("/blog")} data-i18n-cn="阅读档案" data-i18n-en="Read Archive">阅读档案</a>
                    <button class="hero-action" type="button" data-message-open data-i18n-cn="留言给我" data-i18n-en="Message Me">留言给我</button>
                </div>
            </section>

            <section class="bio-col" data-reveal>
                <div class="language-tabs" role="tablist" aria-label="Language">
                    <button id="tab-cn" class="active" type="button" role="tab" aria-selected="true" tabindex="0" data-lang-button="cn" aria-controls="content-cn" data-i18n-cn="中文" data-i18n-en="Chinese">中文</button>
                    <button id="tab-en" type="button" role="tab" aria-selected="false" tabindex="-1" data-lang-button="en" aria-controls="content-en" data-i18n-cn="EN" data-i18n-en="English">EN</button>
                </div>

                <div id="content-cn" class="lang-content active" role="tabpanel" lang="zh-CN" aria-labelledby="tab-cn" data-lang-panel="cn">
                    <p class="lead">
                        我是祝庆，目前正在北京电影学院学习影视技术，致力于影视后期、游戏开发（虚幻引擎）与近代史研究。
                    </p>
                    <ul class="bio-points" aria-label="简介重点">
                        <li>
                            <strong>影视后期流程</strong>
                            <span>三年 ISFVF 国际影展字幕组经验。贯通从剪辑、DaVinci 调色到院线级 DCP 制作与放映的完整标准后期流水线。</span>
                        </li>
                        <li>
                            <strong>游戏开发</strong>
                            <span>专注引擎全流程。曾深度复刻《底特律：化身为人》影视级关卡，会使用 UE5 蓝图、nDisplay LED 虚拟制片及实时渲染流。</span>
                        </li>
                        <li>
                            <strong>数字人创作</strong>
                            <span>全栈数字人管线。掌握基于 Light-Stage（光台）资产到 MetaHuman 的超写实角色重建，高斯泼溅融合作品荣获 2025 行业赛事奖项。</span>
                        </li>
                    </ul>
                    <details class="bio-details">
                        <summary data-label-collapsed="展开完整介绍" data-label-expanded="收起详细介绍"><span class="arrow">▶</span> 展开完整介绍</summary>
                        <div class="bio-details__content">
                            <div class="bio-details__inner">
                                <p>
                                    我一直很着迷于影视后期、虚幻引擎开发和视觉设计之间那个交叉的地带：技术怎样才能更好地服务于故事，又怎样能催生出新的视觉语言。
                                </p>
                                <p>
                                    我在学校 ISFVF 电影节当了三年的字幕组组长，无论是内嵌字幕、XML 外挂字幕，还是自媒体平台的各种发行版本，我都很熟悉。另外，利用学校的放映机资源，我也掌握了 DCP 的制作和放映。能亲手完成电影院放映的最后一环，真的很令人兴奋。
                                </p>
                                <p>
                                    在 UE5 的自学中，我复刻过《底特律：化身为人》的一个章节，也熟悉 nDisplay 虚拟拍摄 LED 背景墙的流程。同时，借助系里的光台资产，我研究了如何把真人复刻成 MetaHuman 数字人。我还做了一个纯原创的作品，结合高斯泼溅与数字人技术，拿到了 2025 年中国创新影像大赛数字人赛道的奖项。游戏技术让我着迷，尤其是过场动画的设计，要是有一天我也能做动画就好了。
                                </p>
                                <p>
                                    在剪辑和调色方面，我有幸参与了一些短片和商业项目的后期制作，合作方包括小红书、国家地理。目前我也在尝试将 3D 立体拍摄、CG 制作与调色流程结合起来：这个过程很有挑战，也让我兴奋。
                                </p>
                            </div>
                        </div>
                    </details>
                    <div class="contact-box">
                        <span>如果你对研究项目、电影制作或技术开发感兴趣，或者只是单纯想聊聊历史与电影之间有意思的事，欢迎通过邮件联系我。我也在寻找影视后期或互动式电影游戏开发方向的工作/实习机会，希望能用我的技能为团队创造价值。</span>
                        <div class="contact-actions">
                            <a href="mailto:zq_eugene@qq.com">zq_eugene@qq.com</a>
                        </div>
                    </div>
                </div>

                <div id="content-en" class="lang-content" role="tabpanel" lang="en" aria-labelledby="tab-en" data-lang-panel="en" hidden>
                    <p class="lead">
                        I am Zhu Qing, currently studying Film and Television Technology at Beijing Film Academy, with a focus on post-production, game development (Unreal Engine), and modern history research.
                    </p>
                    <ul class="bio-points" aria-label="Profile highlights">
                        <li>
                            <strong>Post-production pipeline</strong>
                            <span>Three years of subtitle-team experience at the ISFVF International Film Festival. I work across a standard post-production pipeline, from editing and DaVinci Resolve color grading to cinema-grade DCP creation and screening.</span>
                        </li>
                        <li>
                            <strong>Game development</strong>
                            <span>Focused on the full engine workflow. I have deeply recreated a cinematic level from <em>Detroit: Become Human</em>, and work with UE5 Blueprints, nDisplay LED virtual production, and real-time rendering pipelines.</span>
                        </li>
                        <li>
                            <strong>Digital-human creation</strong>
                            <span>A full-stack digital-human pipeline. I work from Light Stage assets to photoreal MetaHuman reconstruction, and a Gaussian Splatting hybrid project received a 2025 industry competition award.</span>
                        </li>
                    </ul>
                    <details class="bio-details">
                        <summary data-label-collapsed="Read full introduction" data-label-expanded="Collapse full introduction"><span class="arrow">▶</span> Read full introduction</summary>
                        <div class="bio-details__content">
                            <div class="bio-details__inner">
                                <p>
                                    I have long been fascinated by the space where post-production, Unreal Engine development, and visual design overlap: how technology can better serve story, and how it can give rise to new visual languages.
                                </p>
                                <p>
                                    For three years, I led the subtitle team at my school's ISFVF film festival. I am comfortable with embedded subtitles, XML sidecar subtitles, and the many delivery versions required by social media platforms. With access to the academy's projection facilities, I have also learned DCP creation and screening. Completing the final step before a film reaches the cinema screen still feels genuinely exciting.
                                </p>
                                <p>
                                    In my self-directed UE5 practice, I recreated a chapter from <em>Detroit: Become Human</em> and became familiar with nDisplay workflows for LED virtual production backgrounds. Using light-stage assets, I also researched how to reconstruct a real person as a MetaHuman digital human. I created an original work combining Gaussian Splatting and digital-human techniques, which received an award in the Digital Human category at the 2025 China Innovative Image Competition. Game technology fascinates me, especially the design of cinematics, and I hope I can make animation myself someday.
                                </p>
                                <p>
                                    As an editor and colorist, I have been lucky to join post-production on short films and commercial projects, with collaborators including Xiaohongshu and National Geographic. I am now experimenting with combining stereoscopic 3D shooting, CG production, and color workflows: a demanding process, and one that keeps me excited.
                                </p>
                            </div>
                        </div>
                    </details>
                    <div class="contact-box">
                        <span>If you are interested in research projects, filmmaking, or technical development, or if you simply want to talk about the fascinating ties between history and cinema, feel free to email me. I am also looking for work or internship opportunities in post-production or interactive film/game development, where I hope my skills can create value for a team.</span>
                        <div class="contact-actions">
                            <a href="mailto:zq_eugene@qq.com">zq_eugene@qq.com</a>
                        </div>
                    </div>
                </div>
            </section>
        </div>
    </main>

    <div class="message-modal" data-message-modal hidden>
        <div class="message-modal__backdrop" data-message-close></div>
        <section class="message-dialog" role="dialog" aria-modal="true" aria-labelledby="message-title" data-message-dialog>
            <button class="message-close" type="button" aria-label="关闭留言窗口" data-message-close data-aria-cn="关闭留言窗口" data-aria-en="Close message window">×</button>
            <span class="eyebrow">Email Message</span>
            <h2 id="message-title" data-i18n-cn="给我留言" data-i18n-en="Send Me a Message">给我留言</h2>
            <p data-i18n-cn="写下想聊的内容和联系方式，提交后会用你的邮件客户端发给我。" data-i18n-en="Leave your message and contact details. Submitting will open your email client and address it to me.">写下想聊的内容和联系方式，提交后会用你的邮件客户端发给我。</p>
            <form class="message-form" data-message-form>
                <label>
                    <span data-i18n-cn="联系方式" data-i18n-en="Contact">联系方式</span>
                    <input name="contact" type="text" autocomplete="email" placeholder="邮箱 / 微信 / 电话" data-placeholder-cn="邮箱 / 微信 / 电话" data-placeholder-en="Email / WeChat / Phone" required />
                </label>
                <label>
                    <span data-i18n-cn="留言" data-i18n-en="Message">留言</span>
                    <textarea name="message" rows="6" placeholder="想合作的项目、问题，或者只是打个招呼。" data-placeholder-cn="想合作的项目、问题，或者只是打个招呼。" data-placeholder-en="A project idea, a question, or just a quick hello." required></textarea>
                </label>
                <button type="submit" data-i18n-cn="发送到邮箱" data-i18n-en="Send to Email">发送到邮箱</button>
            </form>
            <div class="message-success" data-message-success hidden>
                <h3 data-i18n-cn="发送成功提醒" data-i18n-en="Before You Send">发送成功提醒</h3>
                <p data-i18n-cn="如果邮件客户端已经弹出，请确认发送。为了保险，也建议使用 QQ 邮箱网页版联系我。" data-i18n-en="If your email client has opened, please confirm the message there. You can also use QQ Mail webmail as a backup.">如果邮件客户端已经弹出，请确认发送。为了保险，也建议使用 QQ 邮箱网页版联系我。</p>
                <a class="message-webmail" href="https://mail.qq.com/" target="_blank" rel="noreferrer" data-i18n-cn="打开 QQ 邮箱网页版" data-i18n-en="Open QQ Mail Web">打开 QQ 邮箱网页版</a>
                <label>
                    <span data-i18n-cn="刚刚发送的内容" data-i18n-en="Message Draft">刚刚发送的内容</span>
                    <textarea data-message-copy readonly rows="7"></textarea>
                </label>
                <button type="button" data-message-copy-button data-i18n-cn="复制留言内容" data-i18n-en="Copy Message">复制留言内容</button>
            </div>
        </section>
    </div>

    <script>
        const buttons = Array.from(document.querySelectorAll("[data-lang-button]"));
        const panels = Array.from(document.querySelectorAll("[data-lang-panel]"));
        const modal = document.querySelector("[data-message-modal]");
        const dialog = document.querySelector("[data-message-dialog]");
        const openMessageButtons = document.querySelectorAll("[data-message-open]");
        const closeMessageButtons = document.querySelectorAll("[data-message-close]");
        const messageForm = document.querySelector("[data-message-form]");
        const messageSuccess = document.querySelector("[data-message-success]");
        const messageCopy = document.querySelector("[data-message-copy]");
        const messageCopyButton = document.querySelector("[data-message-copy-button]");
        const pageRoots = document.querySelectorAll("body > main, body > footer, [data-site-header]");
        const bioDetails = Array.from(document.querySelectorAll(".bio-details"));
        const focusableSelector = 'a[href], button:not([disabled]), input:not([disabled]), textarea:not([disabled]), [tabindex]:not([tabindex="-1"])';
        let previousFocus = null;

        const getCurrentLanguage = () => (document.documentElement.dataset.language === "en" ? "en" : "cn");
        const syncDocumentTitle = () => {
            document.title =
                getCurrentLanguage() === "en"
                    ? "Zhu Qing | Post-Production & Unreal Engine Development"
                    : "祝庆 Zhu Qing | 影视后期与 Unreal Engine 开发";
        };

        const setLanguage = (activeButton, options = { persist: true, emit: true }) => {
            const lang = activeButton.getAttribute("data-lang-button");
            document.documentElement.dataset.language = lang;
            document.documentElement.lang = lang === "en" ? "en" : "zh-CN";

            if (options.persist) {
                try {
                    localStorage.setItem("zq-language", lang);
                } catch {}
            }

            buttons.forEach((button) => {
                const active = button === activeButton;
                button.classList.toggle("active", active);
                button.setAttribute("aria-selected", String(active));
                button.tabIndex = active ? 0 : -1;
            });

            panels.forEach((panel) => {
                const active = panel.getAttribute("data-lang-panel") === lang;
                panel.classList.toggle("active", active);
                panel.toggleAttribute("hidden", !active);
            });

            syncDocumentTitle();

            if (options.emit) {
                window.dispatchEvent(new CustomEvent("zq-language-change", { detail: { language: lang } }));
            }
        };

        const initialLanguageButton = buttons.find((button) => button.getAttribute("data-lang-button") === getCurrentLanguage()) || buttons[0];
        if (initialLanguageButton) {
            setLanguage(initialLanguageButton, { persist: false, emit: false });
        }

        buttons.forEach((button, index) => {
            button.addEventListener("click", () => {
                setLanguage(button);
            });

            button.addEventListener("keydown", (event) => {
                if (!["ArrowLeft", "ArrowRight", "Home", "End"].includes(event.key)) return;

                event.preventDefault();
                const nextIndex = {
                    ArrowLeft: (index - 1 + buttons.length) % buttons.length,
                    ArrowRight: (index + 1) % buttons.length,
                    Home: 0,
                    End: buttons.length - 1,
                }[event.key];
                const nextButton = buttons[nextIndex];
                setLanguage(nextButton);
                nextButton.focus();
            });
        });

        bioDetails.forEach((details) => {
            const summary = details.querySelector("summary");
            const content = details.querySelector(".bio-details__content");
            if (!summary || !content) return;

            const setSummaryLabel = (expanded) => {
                const label = expanded ? summary.dataset.labelExpanded : summary.dataset.labelCollapsed;
                const arrow = expanded ? "▼" : "▶";
                summary.innerHTML = `<span class="arrow">${arrow}</span> ${label}`;
                summary.setAttribute("aria-expanded", String(expanded));
            };

            setSummaryLabel(details.open);
            content.style.height = details.open ? `${content.scrollHeight}px` : "0px";
            content.style.opacity = details.open ? "1" : "0";

            summary.addEventListener("click", (event) => {
                event.preventDefault();

                const isOpen = details.hasAttribute("open");
                content.style.overflow = "hidden";

                if (isOpen) {
                    details.dataset.animating = "closing";
                    setSummaryLabel(false);
                    content.style.height = `${content.scrollHeight}px`;
                    content.style.opacity = "1";
                    content.getBoundingClientRect();
                    content.style.height = "0px";
                    content.style.opacity = "0";
                    const finishClosing = (transitionEvent) => {
                        if (transitionEvent.propertyName !== "height") return;
                        details.removeAttribute("open");
                        delete details.dataset.animating;
                        content.removeEventListener("transitionend", finishClosing);
                    };
                    content.addEventListener("transitionend", finishClosing);
                } else {
                    details.dataset.animating = "opening";
                    details.setAttribute("open", "");
                    setSummaryLabel(true);
                    content.style.height = "0px";
                    content.style.opacity = "0";
                    content.getBoundingClientRect();
                    content.style.height = `${content.scrollHeight}px`;
                    content.style.opacity = "1";
                }
            });

            content.addEventListener("transitionend", (event) => {
                if (event.propertyName !== "height") return;
                if (details.open && details.dataset.animating === "opening") {
                    content.style.height = "auto";
                    delete details.dataset.animating;
                }
            });
        });

        const getDialogFocusables = () => Array.from(dialog?.querySelectorAll(focusableSelector) || []).filter((element) => element.offsetParent !== null);
        const getCopyIdleLabel = () => (getCurrentLanguage() === "en" ? "Copy Message" : "复制留言内容");
        const getCopiedLabel = () => (getCurrentLanguage() === "en" ? "Copied" : "已复制");
        const getCopyFallbackLabel = () => (getCurrentLanguage() === "en" ? "Please copy manually" : "请手动复制");

        const openMessageModal = () => {
            previousFocus = document.activeElement;
            modal?.removeAttribute("hidden");
            pageRoots.forEach((item) => item.setAttribute("inert", ""));
            document.body.classList.add("message-modal-open");
            messageForm?.removeAttribute("hidden");
            messageSuccess?.setAttribute("hidden", "");
            if (messageCopyButton) messageCopyButton.textContent = getCopyIdleLabel();
            getDialogFocusables()[0]?.focus();
        };

        const closeMessageModal = () => {
            modal?.setAttribute("hidden", "");
            pageRoots.forEach((item) => item.removeAttribute("inert"));
            document.body.classList.remove("message-modal-open");
            previousFocus?.focus?.();
        };

        openMessageButtons.forEach((button) => button.addEventListener("click", openMessageModal));
        closeMessageButtons.forEach((button) => button.addEventListener("click", closeMessageModal));

        document.addEventListener("keydown", (event) => {
            if (event.key === "Escape" && !modal?.hasAttribute("hidden")) {
                closeMessageModal();
            }

            if (event.key === "Tab" && !modal?.hasAttribute("hidden")) {
                const focusableItems = getDialogFocusables();
                const first = focusableItems[0];
                const last = focusableItems[focusableItems.length - 1];
                if (!first || !last) return;

                if (event.shiftKey && document.activeElement === first) {
                    event.preventDefault();
                    last.focus();
                } else if (!event.shiftKey && document.activeElement === last) {
                    event.preventDefault();
                    first.focus();
                }
            }
        });

        messageForm?.addEventListener("submit", (event) => {
            event.preventDefault();
            const formData = new FormData(messageForm);
            const contact = String(formData.get("contact") || "").trim();
            const message = String(formData.get("message") || "").trim();
            const isEnglish = getCurrentLanguage() === "en";
            const plainMessage = isEnglish
                ? `Recipient: zq_eugene@qq.com\nSubject: Message from personal website\n\nContact: ${contact}\n\nMessage:\n${message}`
                : `收件人：zq_eugene@qq.com\n主题：来自个人网站的留言\n\n联系方式：${contact}\n\n留言：\n${message}`;
            const subject = encodeURIComponent(isEnglish ? "Message from personal website" : "来自个人网站的留言");
            const body = encodeURIComponent(isEnglish ? `Contact: ${contact}\n\nMessage:\n${message}` : `联系方式：${contact}\n\n留言：\n${message}`);
            window.location.href = `mailto:zq_eugene@qq.com?subject=${subject}&body=${body}`;
            if (messageCopy) messageCopy.value = plainMessage;
            messageForm.setAttribute("hidden", "");
            messageSuccess?.removeAttribute("hidden");
            messageCopyButton?.focus();
        });

        messageCopyButton?.addEventListener("click", async () => {
            const text = messageCopy?.value || "";
            try {
                await navigator.clipboard.writeText(text);
                messageCopyButton.textContent = getCopiedLabel();
            } catch {
                messageCopy?.focus();
                messageCopy?.select();
                messageCopyButton.textContent = getCopyFallbackLabel();
            }
        });
    </script>
</BaseLayout>

<style>
    .home-hero {
        position: relative;
        z-index: 10;
        min-height: 100vh;
        display: flex;
        align-items: center;
        padding: calc(var(--header-height) + 56px) var(--page-x) 64px;
    }

    .home-grid {
        width: min(100%, 1280px);
        margin: 0 auto;
        display: grid;
        grid-template-columns: minmax(280px, 0.84fr) minmax(340px, 1.16fr);
        gap: clamp(38px, 7vw, 92px);
        align-items: center;
    }

    .profile-col h1 {
        display: grid;
        gap: 10px;
        margin: 10px 0 24px;
        color: var(--text-main);
        font-family: var(--font-display);
        font-size: clamp(2.2rem, 9.5cqw, 4.15rem);
        line-height: 1.05;
        letter-spacing: 0;
    }

    .profile-col {
        container-type: inline-size;
    }

    .profile-col h1 small {
        color: var(--text-muted);
        font-size: 0.32em;
        font-weight: 680;
        letter-spacing: 0.06em;
        line-height: 1.18;
        text-transform: uppercase;
    }

    :root[data-language="en"] .profile-col h1 {
        gap: 12px;
        line-height: 1.08;
    }

    @supports not (font-size: 1cqw) {
        .profile-col h1 {
            font-size: clamp(2.2rem, 4.6vw, 4.15rem);
        }
    }

    .cinematic-frame {
        width: min(100%, 520px);
        aspect-ratio: 16 / 9;
        margin-bottom: 28px;
        overflow: hidden;
        border: 1px solid var(--border);
        border-radius: 4px;
        background: #111;
        box-shadow: 0 24px 70px rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.52);
    }

    .cinematic-frame img {
        width: 100%;
        height: 100%;
        object-fit: cover;
        filter: saturate(0.82) contrast(1.12) brightness(0.78);
        transition: transform 8s ease, filter 600ms ease;
